<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_134" id="65v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_134_r1l1">Dẏetrichen Stauffer von Erenfels </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r1l2">cʒum Stain </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_134_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Dẏetrich . Als Jr vns <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von herman <expan>Abemberg<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r1l4">des hafners von hewberg ſun ewrs armenmans wegen etc / daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r1l5">haben wir wol vernomen / vnd haben die ~ vnſern darumb </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r1l6">beſendt / . vnd kunnen nicht erfaren / daʒ das dheiner der vnſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r1l7">nicht getan hab / vnd wiſʒen auch darumb nicht / vnd <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r1l9">auch vngern <expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>vah<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> heıſſen </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_134_r1l8">heiſſen </ab></add> cʒu <expan>vnbıllıch<ex>er</ex></expan> vveẏſe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r1l10">Darümb ſo mügt Jr <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> vorſche darnach <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vver </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_134_r1l12">das 
<add><ab facs="#facs_134_r1l11">ſuſt </ab></add> getan hab / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_134" id="65v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Dyetrichen Stauffer von Erenfels czum Stain </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Dyetrich, als ir uns
                                <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Herman
                                <expan>Abemberg<ex>er</ex></expan>, des Hafners von Hewberg sun,
                        ewrs armenmans, wegen etc., daz haben wir wol vernomen und haben die unsern
                        darumb besendt und kunnen nicht erfaren, daz das dheiner der unser nicht
                        getan hab und wiszen auch darumb nicht und <expan>wolte<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        auch ungern <expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vah<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>heissen</add> czu <expan>unbillich<ex>er</ex></expan> weyse; darümb so
                        mügt ir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> vorsche darnach
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wer das <add>sust</add> getan hab.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
